Create your own step challenge
Step challenges are a fun and easy way to get your team happy, moving and motivated in the workplace.
Convert your walking, running and other activities into distance along one of our 300+ virtual routes.
Step CHallenge Features
Talk to a real person
View Screenshots
Our website as well as our iPhone and Android apps allow your participants to get into teams, track their daily step count, compete on leaderboards and move themselves along one of our
300+ virtual maps
.
Creating a fun health initiative is a simple and cost effective way to engage with your employees and increase motivation in the workplace, not to mention that it's a great way of boosting mental and physical wellbeing. With the addition of achievements and team leaderboards you can now help encourage some friendly competition between your teams!
Getting started takes a few minutes and we'll always be happy to help answer any questions you might have about the system.
